      	<div id="post-44945" class="hentry p1 post publish author-Jessica category-awards category-blog category-female-founders category-pitch y2013 m03 d13 h03">
	  <h2 class="entry-title" style="margin-bottom:7px; padding-bottom:0px;"><a href="http://www.women2.com/how-to-deliver-a-winning-tech-conference-pitch/" title="Permalink to How to Deliver a Winning Tech Conference Pitch" rel="bookmark">How to Deliver a Winning Tech Conference Pitch</a></h2>
	  <div class="entry-date" style="font-family:arial; color: #333333; font-size:12px; margin-top:2px; padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:5px;font-weight:bold;"><abbr class="published" title="2013-03-13T10:00:04+0000">Published on: March 13, 2013 <span class="entry-author author vcard" style="display:none;">Posted By <a class="url fn" href="http://www.women2.com/author/jessica/" title="View all posts by Jessica">Jessica</a></span> <span class="entry-author author vcard"> </span></abbr></div>  

